data.name: cboGwa.UserSQL
data.value: SELECT '%', '' FROM SYS.DUAL UNION ALL SELECT A.GWA, A.GWA_NAME FROM BAS0260 A WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = FN_ADM_LOAD_HOSP_CODE() AND A.START_DATE = ( SELECT MAX(X.START_DATE) FROM BAS0260 X WHERE X.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND X.BUSEO_CODE = A.BUSEO_CODE AND X.START_DATE <= TRUNC(SYSDATE) ) ORDER BY 1

data.name: grdOCS6006.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT A.MEMB_GUBUN , A.MEMB , A.CP_CODE , A.CP_PATH_CODE , A.JAEWONIL , A.INPUT_GUBUN , A.PK_SEQ , A.SEQ , A.DIRECT_GUBUN , A.DIRECT_CODE , A.DIRECT_DETAIL , A.HANGMOG_CODE , A.SURYANG , A.NALSU , A.ORD_DANUI , A.BOGYONG_CODE , A.JUSA_CODE , A.JUSA_SPD_GUBUN , A.DV , A.DV_TIME , A.INSULIN_FROM , A.INSULIN_TO , A.TIME_GUBUN , A.BOM_YN , A.BOM_SOURCE_KEY FROM OCS6006 A WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND A.MEMB_GUBUN = :f_memb_gubun AND A.MEMB = :f_memb AND A.CP_CODE = :f_cp_code AND A.CP_PATH_CODE = :f_cp_path_code AND A.JAEWONIL = :f_jaewonil ORDER BY A.PK_SEQ, A.SEQ
